output/
â”œâ”€â”€ sequences/                   # Extracted gene sequences (REAL DNA!)
â”œâ”€â”€ msa/
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ dna_alignments/         # DNA MSAs
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ protein_alignments/     # Protein MSAs
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ noncoding_alignments/   # Promoter MSAs
â”œâ”€â”€ plots/                      # Conservation plots
